to be shocked.

465
00:29:18.490 --> 00:29:21.460
but I sensed. uh.
something else.

466
00:29:22.561 --> 00:29:24.130
They envy you.

467
00:29:24.263 --> 00:29:26.432
Uh. perhaps we-we all do.

468
00:29:26.498 --> 00:29:29.301
