524
00:34:55.827 --> 00:34:59.131
And the conference
is on green energy?

525
00:34:59.265 --> 00:35:00.432
That's nothing.

526
00:35:00.532 --> 00:35:01.976
Next. I got to go
downstairs and listen

527
00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:04.102
