534
00:35:53.385 --> 00:35:55.587
Sounds good.

535
00:36:03.028 --> 00:36:05.531
He's coming downstairs.

536
00:36:06.365 --> 00:36:07.733
Understood.

537
00:36:08.534 --> 00:36:09.668
Popeye's on his way.

538
00:36:09.735 --> 00:36:11.837
I can't believe I'm here.

539
